# ---------- Large reference decks (keep .js source, skip rendered .pptx) ----------
# The Claude reference .pptx files are useful but heavy; commit if you want
# them for parity testing, otherwise they're regeneratable from the .js files.
# Uncomment the next two lines to skip them:
# deck_forge/ai_soc_series_a_pitch.pptx
